# Design System

Full reference: [design-standards.md](mdc:docs/design-standards.md)

## Container

Every section's inner wrapper uses exactly: `mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6`. No other container pattern.

## Colors — Semantic Tokens Only

Never use raw Tailwind colors (`text-stone-500`, `bg-blue-700`) or hex values. Always use the semantic token.

```tsx
// BAD
<p className="text-stone-500">...</p>
<div className="bg-blue-700">...</div>

// GOOD
<p className="text-muted-foreground">...</p>
<div className="bg-primary">...</div>
```

## Spacing

Only use values from the spacing scale in `app/globals.css` section 4. Standard section padding: `py-20 md:py-32`.

## Typography

- Cooper (`font-heading`) for h1 page titles only.
- Inter (default) for everything else — h2 through h6, body, labels.
- One h1 per page. Never skip heading levels (h1 → h3).
- Hero h1: `text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tighter`
- Section h2: `text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tighter`

## Cards

Standard card: `rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4`. Use `shadow-card` for elevation. Do not invent card variants.
